Rating: 4
This recipe was fantastic. I did find it necessary to add a few spices to the flour mixture, as well as the gravy. I would definitely make this again. My fiance loved this too. The gravy was so mouthwaterning and rich in flavor. I do however agree with some of the other cooks on the quantity of butter. The butter should be decreased by at least one quarter. I found that by the end of the meal there was more butter left than bones from the chicken. Served with roasted garlic mashed potatoes and mixed vegetables, this recipe is a super hit!

